19→     * integers representing the indices of the files that were caught by that i-th test
20→     * case in allCases.
21→     */
22→    private final List<Set<Integer>> caseToFiles;
23→
24→    /**
25→     * A set of integers representing the indices of the files that failed one or more
26→     * tests in allCases.
27→     */
28→    private final Set<Integer> wrongSet;
